    step3-forwardвҲҳbackward = funExtвҒ» (QB.quotientImageHomEpi {B = freeBA в„•} {f = вҠҺ.rec fвӮҖ g} (вҹЁ rec-quotient вҹ© , rec-quotient-isSet) step3-forwardвҲҳbackward-ext)

